{
  "stem": "10572.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 43.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't think-- I don't see God as somebody who sits there and manages things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think that [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] he has-- he or she or this being has laid out basic rules.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it is so hard for us to obey them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And I-- I'm deeply touched, constantly, by those who had the, the moral courage [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] of standing up to these evil forces.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think right now of somebody who, to me, was always somebody who-- in the Catholic Church, he would be sainted by now.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's Leo Baeck, Rabbi Baeck, who was the chief rabbi of Berlin, and was taken to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in his arms, two of his sisters died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one day, at the special orders of Eichmann, there was an order out to kill Leo Baeck.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And his name was called out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Baeck answered the call, but not Leo Baeck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was another Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Baeck, a physician.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he knew that one day, he would have to die.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he gave his life for Leo Baeck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And two days before the liberation of Theresienstadt, or three days, Eichmann came to Theresienstadt and found that his orders had been disobeyed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he talked to Baeck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he said, this mistake will be corrected.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then two or three days later, the-- Theresienstadt was liberated, and Baeck was saved.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the press came in and found that Baeck was alive, they came up to this saintly man and said, what should we do?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What should we do with the perpetrators of all this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Baeck looked at them and said, let's go back and teach the book.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And that, I think, is the sign of ultimate greatness and saintliness.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is there anything that you'd like to add briefly that we didn't cover during the interview?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I covered to the-- to the best of my abilities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the-- [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] This is my father, Willy Schurmann, [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] born 1986--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1886, In Pattensen, a little town near Hanover, Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This picture was taken in 1946 in New York.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my mother, Alma Schurmann, nee [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mueller. ?] This picture was taken in Hildesheim, Germany, in 1938.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is Frank Shurman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, his name was Fritz Schurmann.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was taken in Hildesheim in 1938.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] This is my sister Edith Rehfield nee Schurmann.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This picture was taken in 1938 in Hildesheim.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She now lives in Scottsdale, Arizona.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is my younger sister, Hanne-Lore Schurmann, now living as Lore Graham, the widow of the American ambassador Pierre Graham, in Bethesda, Maryland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The picture was taken in 1938 in Hildesheim.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This is the store front of my father's organization in Hildesheim.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He owned a very fine men's store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Picture was taken two days before the liquidation sale started in May-- in May 1938.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This is the picture of Mrs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Augusta Rahr Hamilton, of Manitowoc, Wisconsin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was our angel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Without her we wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was taken a year before her death in 1976.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Manitowoc, Wisconsin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is our wedding picture, both Margie as an ensign in the SPARs Coast Guard Reserve, and Frank Shurman in the uniform of a staff sergeant, but being a special agent in counterintelligence.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The picture was taken by [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ellie ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Marcus ?] in New York, the day of our wedding, the 24th of September, 1945.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] This is after finishing basic training in Camp Lee, Virginia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Private Shurman is ready to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1943.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is in Camp Ashby, Virginia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- the spokesman of Camp Ashby, PW [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mettlach, ?] is being interviewed by the commanding general of the third Service Command, Major General Hayes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Next to General Hayes on the right hand side is Staff Sergeant Shurman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is the commanding general of Third Service Command, Major General Hayes, at somehow a turning point in my military career.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After he left, a few days later, Colonel [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hessler ?] received orders to transfer me from Camp Ashby to Third Service Command into counterintelligence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I then became special agent in counterintelligence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is the memorial in Hildesheim, placed-- the sacred place where our synagogue used to be.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it is a magnificent monument, so beautiful that it is shown in travel books like the Baedeker as the thing to see in Hildesheim.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1988, on the 50th anniversary of Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Margie and I were privileged to be there at its dedication.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was done at [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
